@node SEP
@title "Saucer Seperation"
==============================================================================
                               Saucer Seperation
==============================================================================

When you click on this, you will be asked if you wish to continue...

Presing "Engage" will seperate the two sections of the ship.  
THIS IS A ONE WAY PROCESS.  The screen will shake, then return to normal.

Once seperated, Main power and Torpedoes will be unavailable (because they 
are on the engineering hull, and you are all in the saucer).

Your systems will be in better condition... so, you should be able to get to a
Starbase.  Once there... you will get a new Engineering hull.

@endnode

