@node AWAY
@title "Away teams"
==============================================================================
                                Away Teams
==============================================================================

This sends away teams onto enemy ships.

This will allow you to learn Alien technology.  This will increase your 
weapons power against that enemy.  A percentage will be shown.

This also allows you to steal Power and torpedoes from that enemy.

Once an enemy shiop has been boarded, you will not be able to board it 
again in that turn.  If you attempt to board another races ship, you may 
not learn any more, but you will still be able to steal power/torpedoes.

The enemies sheilds must be below 100 for you to board them!

The technology boost will effect Shields and weapons.

  eg  We learn 10% effectiveness against that enemy.

      Our shields will now be 10% better against that enemy.

      And our Weapons will also be 10% better.

The technology learnt from one race, will not effect another.

@endnode


@node COMMS
@Title "Communications"
==============================================================================
                                  COMMS
==============================================================================

Allows you to communicate with the enemy currently in your sector.  I haven't 
bothered about this part much, since nobody wants to talk to them anyway.

The main use for this is to request docking from that starbase.

After sending your request to the starbase, a new screen will open.  It'll
either allow you to dock, or not.  If the starbace is strong enough, it
will allow you to dock.

@endnode

@node DOCKING
@Title "Docking at Starbases"
==============================================================================
                                Docking
==============================================================================

If clearence was granted, the Docking window will change to the now
familiar more/less display:-

 __________________________  
